When doing a full DB export using connection.createDataSet\(\), DBUnit maps MySQL's TinyInt to a BIT. As a result, MySqlDataTypeFactory maps Bit to BooleanDataType. MySqlDataType should have mapped BIT to DataType.TINYINT.

